{
  "stem": "3012.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely nothing, absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were waiting from one day to the other what will come next.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You, you, you-- we became-- it's apathy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's, it's when you-- when you suspect the worst, and even worse than the worst is happening.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we knew that we couldn't stay at the ghetto, because gradually, in May, while we were in the ghetto, we found out that people on the border areas have been put on trains and shipped out, and we didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then one day we heard that postcards marked Waldsee, W-A-L-D-S-E-E, came saying we are in Waldsee, and we are working.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it turned out, later we found out that by the time the postcards arrived, the very people who wrote the cards went up in smoke already in Auschwitz, or, or somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Most of the people were shipped to Auschwitz from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We heard the word Dachau as, as a political, political-- not even internment camp, some kind of a prison.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the word concentration camp, we just didn't know what it is.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We heard once that in Lublin they, they, they harmed some Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In, in Galicia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- well then, I think it was occupied-- occupied Galicia or Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now it belongs to Russia I think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But something is happening, but we didn't know for sure, and we didn't know the facts.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were only rumors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You were not supposed to-- you were not permitted to listen to the voice of America, which of course we have.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we did until we went to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the ghetto, we didn't have radio.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't have nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From one person to the other.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
